75 (g) The chair of the House committee on racial equity, civil rights shall appoint, on or
76 before December 1, 2024, 2 members, each for a 3 year term.
77 SECTION 3. The executive director of the American Muslim commission, established by
78 section 1, shall initially be appointed by the commissioners for the term of 3 years on or before
79 December 1, 2025.
80 SECTION 4. Sections 1 to 3, inclusive, shall take effect on December 1, 2024.
